real-time 1:1 chat app using React Native (frontend) and Node.js (Express + Socket.IO) backend. Store data in a database (MongoDB/Postgres).

Requirements (MVP)

Auth: Register, Login (JWT-based).

User List: Show all users, tap to start chat.

Chat Screen:

Real-time messaging (Socket.IO).

Messages persist in DB.

Typing indicator.

Online/offline status.

Message delivery/read receipts.

Basic UI:

Auth screens.

Home (user list + last message).

Chat (scrollable messages, input box, typing, ticks).

API & Socket (minimum)

REST:

POST /auth/register, POST /auth/login

GET /users

GET /conversations/:id/messages

Socket events:

message:send → send new msg

message:new → receive msg

typing:start|stop

message:read

Deliverables

GitHub repo with /mobile (React Native) + /server (Node).

README: setup, run, env vars, sample users.

Short demo video (≤5 min).